commits.author: Tomoko Uchida
commits.sourceNew: /** * Returns the character at position pos from the * matched text. * * It is equivalent to yytext().charAt(pos), but faster * * @param pos the position of the character to fetch. * A value from 0 to yylength()-1. * * @return the character at position pos */ public final char yycharat(int pos) { return zzBuffer[zzStartRead+pos]; }
